<plot>A mischievous young boy, Tom Sawyer ('Jonathan Taylor Thomas' (qv)),witnesses a murder by the deadly Injun Joe. Tom becomes friends with Huckleberry Finn ('Brad Renfro' (qv)), a boy with no future and no family. Tom has to choose between honoring a friendship or honoring an oath because the town alcoholic is accused of the murder. Tom and Huck go through several adventures trying to retrieve evidence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?611746</url></doc>
